---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Get Involved â€” Quadball Canada" alternate={{ en: "/get-involved/", fr: "/fr/simpliquer/" }} locale="en">
  <section style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <h1>Get Involved</h1>
    <p>Join the growing quadball community in Canada! Whether you're looking to play, volunteer, referee, or host events, there are many ways to get involved.</p>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2>Find a Team</h2>
      <p>Discover quadball teams across Canada and join a community near you. Teams welcome players of all skill levels and backgrounds.</p>
      <a href="/teams/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: var(--brand-primary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700;">Browse Teams</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2 id="volunteer">Volunteer</h2>
      <p>Help grow the sport by volunteering at events, supporting your local team, or contributing to Quadball Canada initiatives. Volunteers are essential to our community.</p>
      <a href="/volunteer-opportunities/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: var(--brand-primary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700;">View Volunteer Opportunities</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2>Become a Referee</h2>
      <p>Referees are crucial to ensuring fair play and maintaining the integrity of the sport. We offer training and certification programs for aspiring officials.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: var(--brand-primary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700;">Learn About Referee Training</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2 id="host-an-event">Host an Event</h2>
      <p>Interested in bringing quadball to your community? We support organizers who want to host tournaments, clinics, and other events.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: var(--brand-primary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700;">Get Event Hosting Information</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 4rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--bg-secondary, #f8f9fa); border-radius: 12px;">
      <h2>Levels of Play</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Quadball in Canada encompasses various levels of competition and participation:</p>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--brand-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Youth</h3>
        <p>Programs designed for younger players to develop skills, teamwork, and a love for the sport in an age-appropriate setting.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--brand-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Recreational</h3>
        <p>Casual play focused on fun, learning, and community building. Perfect for newcomers and those looking to enjoy the sport in a relaxed environment.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--brand-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Competitive</h3>
        <p>High-level play for teams competing in regional and national championships, with a focus on athletic excellence and strategic gameplay.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--brand-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">National Team</h3>
        <p>Representing Canada on the international stage. Our national teams compete against the best in the world at global tournaments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
